snippet.title: The Movie Channel pak
snippet.description:
The Movie Channel presents,The home of the most REALISTIC fan made movie trailers and Hollywood & Bollywood Movies on YouTube! 

Dear viewers, please support my channel and subscribe to my channel so that my goal of Hundred thousand subscribers can be achieved.
◀◀◀________________▶▶▶

Fan made trailers takes days to create, needs lots of planning. That means it contains clips from other movies, put together with special effects using Wondershare Filmora video editor , Picmaker and VSDC. 

At the end of the end my goal is to bring happiness to fans. Basically to create what Hollywood won't. The more it gets popular the higher chance it may come true!!
